== Problem

*Limitations of LLM's:*
#v(6pt)
- Knowledge is frozen at training time
- Prone to hallucinations on factual questions
- Struggle with domain-specific or rapidly changing knowledge

#v(12pt)
#warn-box[
  Asking an LLM about the weather today?
]
